"1800" b="0" lang="en-US" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Times New Roman" /></a:rPr><a:t>Formalize a context-extraction methodology that converts noisy thread content into normalized input (subject, sender cues, semantic body blocks).</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:endParaRPr lang="en-US" dirty="0" /></a:p><a:p><a:pPr /><a:r><a:rPr sz="1800" b="0" lang="en-US" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Times New Roman" /></a:rPr><a:t>Design an adaptive decision layer that maps task intent (summarize/reply/rewrite/classify) to generation strategy while preserving output consistency.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:endParaRPr lang="en-US" dirty="0" /></a:p><a:p><a:pPr /><a:r><a:rPr sz="1800" b="0" lang="en-US" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Times New Roman" /></a:rPr><a:t>Implement priority scoring and action-item extraction so outputs are decision-oriented, not only text-completion outputs.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:endParaRPr lang="en-US" dirty="0" /></a:p><a:p><a:pPr /><a:r><a:rPr sz="1800" b="0" lang="en-US" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Times New Roman" /></a:rPr><a:t>Evaluate practical productivity gains using response relevance, tone alignment, summary compression quality, and drafting-time reduction.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:endParaRPr lang="en-US" dirty="0" /></a:p><a:p><a:pPr /><a:r><a:rPr sz="1800" b="0" lang="en-US" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Times New Roman" /></a:rPr><a:t>Build an observability loop that records request volume, latency, token estimate, and per-action cost for continuous prompt and routing improvement.</a:t></a:r></a:p></p:txBody></p:sp><p:pic><p:nvPicPr><p:cNvPr id="4" name="Picture 2"><a:extLst><a:ext uri="{FF2B5EF4-FFF2-40B4-BE49-F238E27FC236}"><ns2:creationId id="{57B8A755-68F2-8AE4-8F00-137FC8CAC124}" /></a:ext></a:extLst></p:cNvPr><p:cNvPicPr><a:picLocks noChangeAspect="1" noChangeArrowheads="1" /></p:cNvPicPr><p:nvPr /></p:nvPicPr><p:blipFill><a:blip r:embed="rId2"><a:extLst><a:ext uri="{28A0092B-C50C-407E-A947-70E740481C1C}"><ns4:useLocalDpi val="0" /></a:ext><